title: Creepy Biden Does It Again!
itunes:title: Creepy Biden Does It Again!
description:
Kamala Harris sounds exactly like Trump!

Biden defends discriminating against LGBTQ students!

Rep. Jayapal opposes voting on her own bill!

Phone calls from Senator Joe Manchin, Barack Obama, and Joe Biden!

Featuring Stef Zamorano, Ron Placone, and Mike MacRae!
